{
  "stem": "11771.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "But this accompanied when they-- with such a pleasure, that we are leading-- going to the graves, to the massacre to be killed.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "When everybody was coming, [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] came your time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Time your came.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "[SIGHS] Throwed them whatever you got, the Lithuanian will anyway take from you.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And the dogs was barking-- they were accompanying from each side maybe about four or five dogs from each side, with the Lithuanian.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Couldn't run away-- no way to run away.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "That was a group form before us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "Some guy run away-- they call him, [NON-ENGLISH], they catch.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "They shoot him on the spot.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "He didn't even make it three feet.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this was so tight, you couldn't-- the dogs, they wouldn't allow you to step out a little from the line.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And we came on-- that was, we were already the last group from Wednesday.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "On Wednesday, yes, I think.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we came on-- on the place before the graves was ready, made while we were in the synagogue and in the marketplace, they prepare the graves.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The graves, the Jewish community from Ejszyszki did it by themself, years ago, for protecting.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was an old cemetery, a Jewish cemetery.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the farmers used to let the cattles on in this cemetery to feed them.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we dig the graves around the Jewish community, in order to not to allow the cattles to be on the cemetery.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And now, when they came to the execution, they just make it a little wider and deeper.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This wasn't a big job to do it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they use for that the first group, where they took out Tuesday night, where they sent back a letter.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "A funny letter.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
